473
00:34:34,750 --> 00:34:35,590
Simu.

474
00:35:22,220 --> 00:35:23,060
Bố.

475
00:35:23,470 --> 00:35:24,790
Cha ơi, giúp con với!

476
00:35:25,430 --> 00:35:26,270
Giúp tôi với!

477
00:35:26,480 --> 00:35:27,350
Bố.

478
00:35:27,350 --> 00:35:28,190
Tôi sẽ không giúp bạn.

479
00:35:29,140 --> 00:35:30,060
