Đoàn Xu,

513
00:38:39,830 --> 00:38:40,700
Tôi là He Simu.

514
00:38:41,350 --> 00:38:42,350
Tôi là He Simu.

515
00:38:46,500 --> 00:38:47,340
Cáo,

516
00:38:48,750 --> 00:38:49,590
